    ],
    "text": "An Act To Amend The Judicature Act, No. 2 Of 1978",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      47.99,
      151.7,
      310.7,
      177.17
    ],
    "text": "BE it enacted by the Parliament of the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka as follows: -",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      47.99,
      187.54,
      310.69,
      213.17
    ],
    "text": "1. This Act may be cited as the Judicature (Amendment) Act, No. 8 of 2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      47.99,
      223.54,
      310.71,
      261.17
    ],
    "text": "2. Section 9 of the Judicature Act, No. 2 of 1978 is hereby amended, by the repeal of paragraph (d) of subsection (1) of that section, and substitution therefor, of the following paragraph:-",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.99,
      271.7,
      310.69,
      297.17
    ],
    "text": "\u201c(d) any offence committed by any person on the high seas where-",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      76.99,
      307.7,
      302.83,
      321.17
    ],
    "text": "(i) such offence is piracy by the law of nations; or",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      76.99,
      331.7,
      310.7,
      405.17
    ],
    "text": "(ii) such offence is an offence under the Poisons, Opium and Dangerous Drugs Ordinance (Chapter 218), Conventions Against Illicit Traffic in Narcotic Drugs and Psychotropic Substances Act, No. 1 of 2008 or any such written law;\u201d.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      47.99,
      415.54,
      310.69,
      441.17
    ],
    "text": "3. In the event of any inconsistency between the Sinhala and Tamil texts of this Act, the Sinhala text shall prevail.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
